GET     /admin/users                    [DONE]
        -> View All Users (Students + Drivers + Admins)
        -> Optional query param: ?role=STUDENT / DRIVER / ADMIN
        -> Returns: List of user details

POST    /admin/users                    [DONE]
        -> Admin adds a new User / Driver / Admin directly
        -> No OTP verification required
        -> verified = true, enabled = true set automatically
        -> Role specified in request body (STUDENT / DRIVER / ADMIN)

PATCH   /admin/users/{userId}/suspend   [DONE]
        -> Suspend a User / Driver / Admin
        -> Sets enabled = false
        -> User is immediately locked out of all @VerifiedUser endpoints

PATCH   /admin/users/{userId}/unsuspend [PENDING]
        -> Unsuspend a User / Driver / Admin
        -> Sets enabled = true
        -> User regains access to all @VerifiedUser endpoints
